{"tid":337993,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"娘娘杜小喬唔再收兵　主動拖手表白","createTime":"2017-07-27T19:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T13:02:38.000Z","uid":14730,"like":2,"dislike":304,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6129b80172137c69cf318ed22d1cb33d63073ef","tid":337993,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T19:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/030037_2aef24801311aeab0ec2c306c3f529f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F030037_2aef24801311aeab0ec2c306c3f529f8.jpg&h=f556b3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網絡紅人杜小喬常被網民稱為「娘娘」，並傳聞這位女神「收兵」無數，而日前她竟然主動與男仔拖手表白，是不是表示她要終結「收兵生涯」呢，所有排隊中的兵都要各散東西呢？其實這是《前度》的劇情的內容，劇中的美玉（杜小喬飾）相約同事大衛去看恐怖電影，然後藉詞拖手。<br />\n<br />\n二人看完電影後散步，娘娘杜小喬便主動連番追問：「你覺得我為人如何？」「如果有一個像我這樣的女仔做你的女朋友，好不好？」首次看到娘娘主動表白，身為兵的一分子該會感到有點心酸吧，而杜小喬則在社交網表示這是「浪漫恐怖片」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2v3h7Ir\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2v3h7Ir&d=5f8aTq4Pbr%2B9gATaFqyk6Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e32fd0e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2v3h7Ir</a>"},{"pid":"f212fca5aab8ae6ebb53cf479ed9eb1fbeef3b50","tid":337993,"uid":90247,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T20:43:01.000Z","msg":"拍完套野咪繼續做兵囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fed84ca932a9cdfe17c61f08aa6cf3855bcf28a","tid":337993,"uid":117901,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T20:44:13.000Z","msg":"低質打手"},{"pid":"48036a27178f2ec66554860eb56252e0f8fd5993","tid":337993,"uid":17761,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T21:01:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪標題黨"},{"pid":"55cdd66f7e5cd981b492a5c5a05e032896f7af30","tid":337993,"uid":101328,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T21:58:26.000Z","msg":"點解佢同Lulu 咁撚普通都可以做到娘娘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class